      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 128: While `tempAccount` is nil, every auth event from every account is appended to `pendingAuthResults`. On an app with active account/device activity, this can grow unnecessarily and retains unrelated callback details until temporary account creation finishes. Prefer filtering to only device-auth events relevant to this flow if possible, or bound/clear the buffer on terminal states and cancellation. For example, buffer only states expected before the temporary account id is known and discard unrelated terminal/error events once `startGeneration` changes.",
